// Business Primitives

# Product id score price

: double_price p
    💰* ⚓ p 💰2.00

: is_high_score id score price
    > ⚓ score 500

: main
    L p N Product 3
    . S ⚓ p id 0 1
    . S ⚓ p score 0 100
    . S ⚓ p price 0 💰10.00
    . S ⚓ p id 1 2
    . S ⚓ p score 1 600
    . S ⚓ p price 1 💰20.00
    . S ⚓ p id 2 3
    . S ⚓ p score 2 400
    . S ⚓ p price 2 💰30.00
    L doubled ⟴ ⮞ p "price" double_price
    . ? = G ⚓ doubled price 1 💰40.00
        0
        🚨 "Map failed"
    L high ▽ ⮞ doubled is_high_score
    . ? = ℓ ⚓ high 1
        0
        🚨 "Filter count failed"
    . ? = G ⚓ high id 0 2
        0
        🚨 "Filter content failed"
    . ? ≈ 💰🧵 G ⚓ high price 0 "40.0000"
        0
        🚨 "MoneyStr failed"
    L home 🌍 "HOME"
    ? > ℓ ⮞ home 0
        0
        🚨 "Env failed"
